measurements.description: Three hundred twenty-two flowers and six buds on 23 up-to 15-cm inflorescences; well displayed around a cleanly grown 38-cm wide x 23-cm tall plant grown in bark in a 10-cm plastic pot; sepals and petals cream white overlaid pink, blotched dark rose; lip saccate, yellow, rose band at midpoint; anther cap white; substance avearage; texture diamond dust; commended for excellent culture in a small pot.
